dct_description_sm: Outer cover of a 1975-1976 map directory of Passaic, N.J. with street index, published by the Passaic Area Chamber of Commerce. Back of map consists of various advertisements, a town history, municipal phone numbers and chamber officers and directors.
dct_publisher_sm: The Passaic Area Chamber of Commerce
